OL,5, Retailers John Lewis and DFS have said 
OL,6, customers are cutting back on the      
OL,7, amount they spend due to the rising    
OL,8, cost of living.                        
OL,10,FJohn Lewis said while shopper numbers  
OL,11,Fwere higher than last year, customers  
OL,12,Fwere spending less and avoiding buying 
OL,13,Fas many "big ticket" items.            
OL,15,F"No one could have predicted the scale 
OL,16,Fof the cost of living crisis," said    
OL,17,FJohn Lewis boss Dame Sharon White.     
OL,19,FThe company reported a loss of #99m for
OL,20,Fthe first half of its trading year.    
